<subSubSection id="A2155EA5A0FA3BAB21C705F3F55181A4" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="720AE394543D86E1FF847423C65FFA13" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph id="25B6C445AFAE579B069AF98DE667D77B" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">
New records: East Rhodopes: Pastrook vill., sweeping, 2 w., leg. I. Gjonov; Strazhets vill., 05.09.2010, 4 w., leg. ALG; Kazak vill., 05.09.2010, 11 w., leg. ALG; Meden buk vill., 09.04.2013, 11 w., leg. ALG; Madzharovo, Gluhite kamani loc., 11.04.2013, 1 w., leg. ALG; Svirachi vill., 22.04.2014, 10 w., leg. ALG; Vetrushka vill., 01.06.2015, 1 w., leg. ALG; Sakar Mt., Mihalich vill., 03.05.2019, 20 w., leg. ALG; Struma Valley, Lebnitsa vill., 06.08.2019, light trap, 1 q., leg. ALG; Besapari hills, Isperihovo vill., 12.04.2021, 25 w., leg. ALG. Detailed occurrence data: 
<bibRefCitation id="3AA4CA786AE20C5C4167D774CA1C0667" author="Lapeva-Gjonova, A." journalOrPublisher="Biodiversity Data Journal" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" refId="B7741022" refString="Lapeva-Gjonova, A., Borowiec, L., 2022. New and little-known ant species (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) from Bulgaria. In: Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." title="New and little-known ant species (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) from Bulgaria" volumeTitle="Biodiversity Data Journal. Occurrence dataset." year="2022">Lapeva-Gjonova and Borowiec (2022)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="4BA11DD3767E6B3114310148C0514CA7" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" type="notes">
<paragraph id="336F6CB9A0AF99E968E2189201D770D1" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="57D1277E4DCCE35BCC83925EBB699BEC" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">
This species is known from the north-eastern and eastern Mediterranean regions. The records of 
<taxonomicName id="BE45AED13DAB52ED6ECF3365F3755A2E" authorityName="Emery" authorityYear="1869" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Crematogaster" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Crematogaster auberti" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="auberti">
<emphasis id="CFF09E5A71B63C9726F42BC83CC91239" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Crematogaster auberti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Emery, 1869 from Struma Valley in Bulgaria (
<bibRefCitation id="21B9CC0AFE1CD9EFD5E17BEFDB9F7491" author="Lapeva-Gjonova, A." journalOrPublisher="Myrmecological News" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" pagination="1 - 3" refId="B7725822" refString="Lapeva-Gjonova, A., 2011. First records of three ant species (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) from Bulgaria. Myrmecological News 14: 1 - 3" title="First records of three ant species (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) from Bulgaria" volume="14" year="2011">Lapeva-Gjonova 2011</bibRefCitation>
) should be assigned to 
<taxonomicName id="6A618F4E756F537A281A552CB82C2D1C" class="Insecta" genus="C." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="C. lorteti" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lorteti">
<emphasis id="27FE5CDB0EBFF541D4CB37F7FB40EDCD" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">C. lorteti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
